    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>[Congressional Record Volume 161, Number 34 (Friday, February 27, 2015)]From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. STUTZMAN:H.R. 1160.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Article I, Section 8 of the U.S. Constitution which states,``Congress shall have the power . . . to regulate commercewith foreign nations, and among the several states and amongthe Indian Tribes.''[Page H1500]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
